  "texts": [
    "These mask tokens are also trained through back-propagation.",
    "Only a small subset of the remaining frames, which are not masked, is used as input for the encoder.",
    "This lightweight mechanism allows for efficient processing.",
    "The output of the encoder is then combined with the masked projections and fed into a lightweight decoder.MAE aims to minimize the difference between the original inputs and the reconstructed outputs.",
    "By reconstructing the original input with only a partial view, MAE effectively learns to capture and encode crucial information."
  ],
